WEBVTT

00:00:03.520 --> 00:00:05.829
Well, good evening, everybody. Thank you

00:00:05.839 --> 00:00:09.430
for joining us again tonight. Sorry

00:00:09.440 --> 00:00:13.270
I'm late. I had a lot to do today.

00:00:13.280 --> 00:00:14.870
I'm going to go over a little bit of

00:00:14.880 --> 00:00:16.310
some of the things the Lord showed us

00:00:16.320 --> 00:00:19.830
yesterday in prayer, and we'll see if

00:00:19.840 --> 00:00:22.150
Braden had time to look at any news

00:00:22.160 --> 00:00:23.910
to see if there's any news or whatever.

00:00:23.920 --> 00:00:25.590
But we're just going to pray tonight.

00:00:25.600 --> 00:00:27.349
We're going to pray for our

00:00:27.359 --> 00:00:31.589
troops. As Iran says if they have a ground

00:00:31.589 --> 00:00:31.599
invasion,

00:00:31.599 --> 00:00:33.190
"We're going to burn them

00:00:33.190 --> 00:00:33.200
alive,"and

00:00:33.200 --> 00:00:34.950
the things that they're saying. I

00:00:34.960 --> 00:00:36.870
say, "No, you're not.

00:00:36.880 --> 00:00:38.630
We're not going to allow that. We're

00:00:38.640 --> 00:00:39.990
going to protect them in the

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:42.310
spirit. We're

00:00:42.320 --> 00:00:43.750
going to protect them in the

00:00:43.750 --> 00:00:43.760
natural."You

00:00:43.760 --> 00:00:46.630
know, and I truly believe that as we

00:00:46.640 --> 00:00:48.549
come together tonight, we can change

00:00:48.559 --> 00:00:52.950
things. As I was praying today, I

00:00:52.960 --> 00:00:56.470
spent most of the day in prayer.

00:00:56.480 --> 00:00:59.990
I was looking clear into July a lot, and

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:02.150
I kept going into July, and I kept

00:01:02.160 --> 00:01:04.229
praying around July. And

00:01:04.239 --> 00:01:06.390
regardless, I'm going to be

00:01:06.400 --> 00:01:09.830
real with you for what I keep seeing:

00:01:09.840 --> 00:01:13.910
this is not going to end fast.

00:01:13.920 --> 00:01:16.149
This is something that they'll try to draw

00:01:16.159 --> 00:01:19.670
out clear into the summer, late summer,

00:01:19.680 --> 00:01:23.910
to try to keep escalating for midterms.

00:01:23.920 --> 00:01:25.830
There's something more sinister behind

00:01:25.840 --> 00:01:29.109
it. But when I'm seeing it concerning

00:01:29.119 --> 00:01:32.230
midterms, praying over our troops on the

00:01:32.240 --> 00:01:36.230
ground, praying over strikes on

00:01:36.240 --> 00:01:39.030
our own bases, and continuing to pray

00:01:39.040 --> 00:01:42.710
over these lone wolf attacks and for our

00:01:42.720 --> 00:01:45.030
own

00:01:45.040 --> 00:01:47.429
electric grid, all the things concerning

00:01:47.439 --> 00:01:51.109
America, there's a lot here. And as I

00:01:51.119 --> 00:01:53.190
was praying into it, it's a lot. I

00:01:53.200 --> 00:01:55.749
told you I was talking to

00:01:55.759 --> 00:01:58.389
Diana as we were praying today,

00:01:58.399 --> 00:02:03.910
and I was really pushing hard because

00:02:03.920 --> 00:02:07.670
I know after I had that visitation from

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:10.229
Sister Lucy that went

00:02:10.239 --> 00:02:12.150
home to be with the Lord in heaven,

00:02:12.150 --> 00:02:12.160
and

00:02:12.160 --> 00:02:16.229
Brother Hagin, the

00:02:16.239 --> 00:02:19.510
things they told me, I was

00:02:19.520 --> 00:02:21.589
practicing it today and really jumping

00:02:21.599 --> 00:02:23.350
in the rivers. And I want to say this

00:02:23.360 --> 00:02:25.110
right off the bat: there's a lot of

00:02:25.120 --> 00:02:26.710
people who said, "Brandon, you're talking to

00:02:26.720 --> 00:02:28.949
the dead. You're

00:02:28.959 --> 00:02:32.470
talking to familiar

00:02:32.480 --> 00:02:34.150
spirits."No,

00:02:34.160 --> 00:02:38.229
no. I went through a portal to heaven,

00:02:38.239 --> 00:02:40.309
where I believe that I'll be one

00:02:40.319 --> 00:02:44.070
day. And if the Lord tarries, if

00:02:44.080 --> 00:02:46.309
somebody was to need to speak to me and

00:02:46.319 --> 00:02:48.229
have a word over there, and it was

00:02:48.239 --> 00:02:51.430
direction from things that were in

00:02:51.440 --> 00:02:53.830
when they were on the earth or whatever,

00:02:53.840 --> 00:02:56.869
the messages from the Lord, this

00:02:56.879 --> 00:02:59.030
isn't demonic.

00:02:59.040 --> 00:03:00.869
Some people are like, "Brandon,

00:03:00.879 --> 00:03:02.229
you're talking to familiar spirits.

00:03:02.239 --> 00:03:04.149
You're talking to the

00:03:04.149 --> 00:03:04.159
dead."And

00:03:04.159 --> 00:03:05.910
I said, "No, this is

00:03:05.910 --> 00:03:05.920
ignorance."Brandon

00:03:05.920 --> 00:03:08.149
would be the last

00:03:08.159 --> 00:03:09.750
person, I'm going to tell you. I know the

00:03:09.760 --> 00:03:11.990
difference. And when the glory of the

00:03:12.000 --> 00:03:14.390
Lord's there, and you're in a portal, and

00:03:14.400 --> 00:03:16.710
you're talking to people that are in

00:03:16.720 --> 00:03:18.309
heaven, and you're hearing the holy angel

00:03:18.319 --> 00:03:21.190
choirs, and you're experiencing the beautiful

00:03:21.200 --> 00:03:25.030
fragrance of heaven,

00:03:25.040 --> 00:03:27.670
there's nothing demonic about it. Now,

00:03:27.680 --> 00:03:29.910
you talking to Cousin George in your

00:03:29.920 --> 00:03:32.149
house, and you're walking around talking

00:03:32.159 --> 00:03:33.910
and hearing voices in your home and

00:03:33.920 --> 00:03:35.430
knocking, you know, that's just

00:03:35.440 --> 00:03:37.350
Casper that's over there, and

00:03:37.360 --> 00:03:39.270
he's knocking on the door over there.

00:03:39.280 --> 00:03:40.789
You know, "Oh, that was

00:03:40.799 --> 00:03:43.509
Grandpa. He's just

00:03:43.509 --> 00:03:43.519
visiting."That's

00:03:43.519 --> 00:03:46.309
a demonic spirit.

00:03:46.319 --> 00:03:48.229
To be absent from the body is to be

00:03:48.239 --> 00:03:50.390
present with the Lord.

00:03:50.400 --> 00:03:52.229
The moment you die, either you're in

00:03:52.239 --> 00:03:54.630
heaven or you're going to hell. There is

00:03:54.640 --> 00:03:56.470
no in-between. There's no purgatory.

00:03:56.480 --> 00:03:58.309
There's nothing. To be absent

00:03:58.319 --> 00:04:00.309
from the body is to be present with the

00:04:00.319 --> 00:04:02.149
Lord,

00:04:02.159 --> 00:04:05.670
or you're in hell. But I want to tell

00:04:05.680 --> 00:04:09.910
you, when you are able to go

00:04:09.920 --> 00:04:12.390
in the spirit into heaven, and see into

00:04:12.400 --> 00:04:14.550
heaven, and see the things that the Lord

00:04:14.560 --> 00:04:17.590
has for us, like even the disciples

00:04:17.600 --> 00:04:22.790
did. You know,

00:04:22.800 --> 00:04:27.110
the Book of Revelation talks all about

00:04:27.120 --> 00:04:29.189
what he was shown in a vision, and the

00:04:29.199 --> 00:04:30.790
things that he had, I believe, an

00:04:30.790 --> 00:04:30.800
out-of-body

00:04:30.800 --> 00:04:33.030
experience,

00:04:33.040 --> 00:04:36.390
with the Father showing him

00:04:36.400 --> 00:04:39.110
everything about heaven. There were a lot

00:04:39.120 --> 00:04:42.310
of things in tribulation, and

00:04:42.320 --> 00:04:46.230
we're talking over 2,000 years ago. He

00:04:46.240 --> 00:04:48.150
didn't know what he was seeing. But

00:04:48.160 --> 00:04:50.390
when you're looking

00:04:50.400 --> 00:04:52.230
over, and the Lord's

00:04:52.240 --> 00:04:54.390
allowing you to look over, it's so

00:04:54.400 --> 00:04:55.749
real and it's right in front of your

00:04:55.759 --> 00:04:59.909
face. And so,

00:04:59.919 --> 00:05:01.590
a lot of people don't know what

00:05:01.590 --> 00:05:01.600
travail

00:05:01.600 --> 00:05:04.629
is. I didn't realize

00:05:04.639 --> 00:05:07.029
when the Lord said to me, "I want you to

00:05:07.039 --> 00:05:09.990
go on YouTube and teach people

00:05:09.990 --> 00:05:10.000
prayer."And

00:05:10.000 --> 00:05:12.550
I knew there were a lot of veterans

00:05:12.560 --> 00:05:15.350
that were joining up with the WWPs, with

00:05:15.360 --> 00:05:17.909
Billy's group. There are a lot of

00:05:17.919 --> 00:05:19.430
WWPs,

00:05:19.440 --> 00:05:22.469
Worldwide Prayers, that come over

00:05:22.479 --> 00:05:25.749
here. But I have a lot of babies, a lot

00:05:25.759 --> 00:05:28.150
of people. And if you remember when

00:05:28.160 --> 00:05:31.430
I told you I didn't want to do this,

00:05:31.440 --> 00:05:33.990
I was walking out, and there was a

00:05:34.000 --> 00:05:37.270
huge auditorium that was a school. It

00:05:37.280 --> 00:05:41.510
was a school, but it was a PE

00:05:41.520 --> 00:05:43.110
room, like where you go and do physical

00:05:43.120 --> 00:05:45.029
education in your school, where it

00:05:45.039 --> 00:05:46.870
would be a cafeteria or whatever, but

00:05:46.880 --> 00:05:48.710
it's cleared out for physical

00:05:48.720 --> 00:05:51.990
education classes at school, PE class.

00:05:53.759 --> 00:05:57.270
I was at a school, and there

00:05:57.270 --> 00:05:57.280
were

00:05:57.280 --> 00:05:59.350
little children everywhere at the school,

00:05:59.360 --> 00:06:01.350
and the Lord said, "Teach my people to

00:06:01.350 --> 00:06:01.360
pray."And

00:06:01.360 --> 00:06:03.110
I said, "No, I don't want

00:06:03.110 --> 00:06:03.120
to."I

00:06:03.120 --> 00:06:06.710
walked out in this dream,

00:06:06.720 --> 00:06:09.510
and I walked out of this vast

00:06:09.520 --> 00:06:11.270
auditorium because I was hurt. I was

00:06:11.280 --> 00:06:15.430
offended by the church, and I was

00:06:15.440 --> 00:06:18.790
turned around by a whirlwind.

00:06:18.800 --> 00:06:22.550
And I could see in the sky the moon

00:06:22.560 --> 00:06:24.790
was divided in half with an

00:06:24.800 --> 00:06:26.950
eclipse. Actually, it was the sun. It was an

00:06:26.960 --> 00:06:28.550
eclipse. It wasn't the moon; it was the

00:06:28.560 --> 00:06:30.710
sun that was an eclipse. I could see it

00:06:30.720 --> 00:06:32.469
was almost completely blacked out. I

00:06:32.479 --> 00:06:34.629
could hear the sirens blowing all around

00:06:34.639 --> 00:06:37.430
me. And I could see the sky

00:06:37.440 --> 00:06:39.590
was divided with black and

00:06:39.600 --> 00:06:42.870
blue. It was

00:06:42.880 --> 00:06:45.350
completely blacked out, and one side of

00:06:45.360 --> 00:06:46.870
the sky was completely blue, and I could

00:06:46.880 --> 00:06:50.070
hear tornado sirens, and I knew there

00:06:50.080 --> 00:06:51.990
was something very wrong. And he said,

00:06:52.000 --> 00:06:56.950
"Go in and teach the children to

00:06:56.950 --> 00:06:56.960
pray."So

00:06:56.960 --> 00:06:59.830
I went into the cafeteria

00:06:59.840 --> 00:07:02.710
where everybody was at, and everybody

00:07:02.720 --> 00:07:04.469
started sitting around me, and there

00:07:04.469 --> 00:07:04.479
were

00:07:04.479 --> 00:07:06.870
kids all around me, and he said, "Teach

00:07:06.870 --> 00:07:06.880
them."So

00:07:06.880 --> 00:07:09.270
I started teaching prayer

00:07:09.280 --> 00:07:13.990
in this vast auditorium full of children,

00:07:14.000 --> 00:07:19.510
and I woke up. I knew then the

00:07:19.510 --> 00:07:19.520
Lord—I

00:07:19.520 --> 00:07:21.430
said, "Lord, how do I

00:07:21.440 --> 00:07:22.790
teach people to pray? I don't even know

00:07:22.800 --> 00:07:24.550
what I'm doing. What do you want me to

00:07:24.550 --> 00:07:24.560
do?"He

00:07:24.560 --> 00:07:28.710
said, "By example.

00:07:28.720 --> 00:07:31.029
Show them how to enter into the rivers,

00:07:31.039 --> 00:07:34.550
how you've learned from people, from

00:07:34.560 --> 00:07:37.990
Pastor Terry and Gina."And there

00:07:38.000 --> 00:07:41.189
were so many that I learned from, Iva.

00:07:41.199 --> 00:07:45.350
They all led prayer, and

00:07:45.360 --> 00:07:47.670
I would listen working for the

00:07:47.680 --> 00:07:50.469
ministry. I was in the back, and I would

00:07:50.479 --> 00:07:52.309
listen to Pastor Terry.

00:07:52.319 --> 00:07:54.550
They would have prayer

00:07:54.560 --> 00:07:57.589
on

00:07:57.599 --> 00:07:59.749
Thursdays. Mondays was healing school,

00:07:59.759 --> 00:08:01.270
and I listened to that, and there

00:08:01.270 --> 00:08:01.280
were

00:08:01.280 --> 00:08:03.029
pastors leading healing school

00:08:03.039 --> 00:08:05.029
and praying for the sick and stuff

00:08:05.039 --> 00:08:07.589
on Mondays. On Thursdays, they

00:08:07.599 --> 00:08:11.430
had prayer school. So I would clean

00:08:11.440 --> 00:08:15.350
and mop the foyer, and vacuum,

00:08:15.360 --> 00:08:17.670
and do prayer. They did prayer on

00:08:17.670 --> 00:08:17.680
Thursdays,

00:08:17.680 --> 00:08:19.510
and I would hear a lady

00:08:19.520 --> 00:08:21.670
named Annie; she was there and she would do

00:08:21.680 --> 00:08:25.510
prayer. There were several others.

00:08:25.520 --> 00:08:27.749
But every Thursday, I would

00:08:27.749 --> 00:08:27.759
take

00:08:27.759 --> 00:08:29.830
my breaks around. Me and a lady named

00:08:29.840 --> 00:08:33.110
Jan, she would clean with me,

00:08:33.120 --> 00:08:35.190
and we would clean the church together,

00:08:35.200 --> 00:08:38.149
and I was the church mouse. I stayed in

00:08:38.159 --> 00:08:40.550
there and I cleaned the nurseries. But I

00:08:40.560 --> 00:08:42.550
would listen to Brother Hagin, and I

00:08:42.560 --> 00:08:44.710
would listen to Pastor Terry, and I would

00:08:44.720 --> 00:08:47.190
listen to these others continually on

00:08:47.190 --> 00:08:47.200
Thursdays,

00:08:47.200 --> 00:08:48.630
and that's where I

00:08:48.640 --> 00:08:51.509
learned prayer. I

00:08:51.519 --> 00:08:54.710
worked there for over four years, and I

00:08:54.720 --> 00:08:56.230
listened to the prayer

00:08:56.240 --> 00:09:01.670
every Thursday,

00:09:01.680 --> 00:09:05.030
and I just kept developing and

00:09:05.040 --> 00:09:06.710
kept developing. And then whenever I quit,

00:09:06.720 --> 00:09:08.470
I thought, "Man, I'm going into full-time

00:09:08.470 --> 00:09:08.480
ministry."And

00:09:08.480 --> 00:09:09.750
the Lord said, "No, you're

00:09:09.760 --> 00:09:11.190
going to be an armor bearer for the

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:14.070
pastor in Oklahoma City."So, I went

00:09:14.080 --> 00:09:16.550
to Oklahoma City, and the Lord had me

00:09:16.560 --> 00:09:19.190
there for 13 years praying, and I did

00:09:19.200 --> 00:09:22.310
Saturday morning prayer, and I just

00:09:22.320 --> 00:09:25.670
kept working at it and working at it.

00:09:25.680 --> 00:09:28.790
There'd be, you know, 100 people show up,

00:09:28.800 --> 00:09:32.230
if that; sometimes less than 20 because

00:09:32.240 --> 00:09:33.670
it was early in the mornings on

00:09:33.680 --> 00:09:37.030
Saturdays. Long story short, I thought

00:09:37.040 --> 00:09:39.829
that was the dream until the Lord

00:09:39.839 --> 00:09:41.829
said, "I want you to go on YouTube and

00:09:41.839 --> 00:09:43.509
tell them the things that I have showed

00:09:43.509 --> 00:09:43.519
you."But

00:09:43.519 --> 00:09:45.670
then he said, "I don't want you

00:09:45.680 --> 00:09:46.870
to do that anymore. I want you to do

00:09:46.880 --> 00:09:50.150
prayer every single time."And I thought,

00:09:50.160 --> 00:09:52.870
"There is nobody going to come and pray

00:09:52.880 --> 00:09:55.430
on YouTube."I mean, in my mind,

00:09:55.440 --> 00:09:56.870
that's what I'm thinking. I'm not vocalizing

00:09:56.870 --> 00:09:56.880
that;

00:09:56.880 --> 00:09:58.630
I'm

00:09:58.640 --> 00:10:01.190
saying it

00:10:01.200 --> 00:10:02.870
in my mind. And I know he hears your

00:10:02.880 --> 00:10:04.710
thoughts, but I was thinking, "Nobody's

00:10:04.720 --> 00:10:06.389
going to show up and pray. Why would

00:10:06.399 --> 00:10:10.470
anybody come and pray on

00:10:10.470 --> 00:10:10.480
YouTube?"But

00:10:10.480 --> 00:10:12.070
he said, "I want you to go live, and

00:10:12.080 --> 00:10:13.990
I want you to start doing these live

00:10:14.000 --> 00:10:18.230
prayer sessions."I was so nervous

00:10:18.240 --> 00:10:20.389
when I first did my first one. I

00:10:20.399 --> 00:10:22.949
created a "Pray With Me"by Kenneth

00:10:22.949 --> 00:10:22.959
E. Hagin,

00:10:22.959 --> 00:10:26.069
and it

00:10:26.079 --> 00:10:28.630
went viral, and then everybody and their

00:10:28.640 --> 00:10:30.949
brother copied it and put it all over.

00:10:30.959 --> 00:10:33.509
All the original "Pray With Me"that you

00:10:33.519 --> 00:10:35.350
see on there, "Pray with Kenneth Hagin for

00:10:35.360 --> 00:10:37.750
30 minutes,"came from my idea that I

00:10:37.760 --> 00:10:40.949
got from the Holy Spirit. I created that,

00:10:40.959 --> 00:10:42.790
and then the ministry took it down

00:10:42.800 --> 00:10:44.949
because I had over a million hits and

00:10:44.959 --> 00:10:47.430
they didn't want that. So they took

00:10:47.440 --> 00:10:49.750
that video down, but then it was

00:10:49.760 --> 00:10:51.509
spread so much, it was all around the

00:10:51.519 --> 00:10:54.790
world. So every one of those is an

00:10:54.800 --> 00:10:58.069
original from me creating it back then

00:10:58.079 --> 00:10:59.670
because I didn't know how to pray by

00:10:59.680 --> 00:11:02.150
myself on the internet.

00:11:02.160 --> 00:11:04.389
And so I started taking Sister Lynn and

00:11:04.399 --> 00:11:05.910
some of these other ministries, and I

00:11:05.920 --> 00:11:07.829
started making "Pray With Me."Then the

00:11:07.839 --> 00:11:09.750
Lord said, "You're done with those.

00:11:09.760 --> 00:11:11.910
You're to pray by yourself now."And I

00:11:11.920 --> 00:11:14.550
thought, "Pray by myself now? How am I

00:11:14.560 --> 00:11:15.990
going to do that?"He said, "Just do

00:11:15.990 --> 00:11:16.000
it."So,

00:11:16.000 --> 00:11:19.430
I did that for about, what was

00:11:19.440 --> 00:11:22.790
it, six months, praying by myself?

00:11:22.790 --> 00:11:22.800
I'd

00:11:22.800 --> 00:11:24.389
been praying with the others for about

00:11:24.399 --> 00:11:26.389
six months, Braden.

00:11:26.399 --> 00:11:29.110
Yeah. And so, we did that.

00:11:29.120 --> 00:11:30.710
I did that, and you'll see the videos.

00:11:30.720 --> 00:11:32.870
Some of them are still there. But then

00:11:32.880 --> 00:11:35.430
the Lord said, "I want you

00:11:35.440 --> 00:11:38.230
to go on live by yourself."So, I

00:11:38.240 --> 00:11:39.590
thought, "I can't do this. I'm taking

00:11:39.600 --> 00:11:42.150
the training wheels

00:11:42.150 --> 00:11:42.160
off."And

00:11:42.160 --> 00:11:44.069
so, that's where we are now. A

